There is a table:
table name = lemda_table
db name = lemda_db
==========================
Id   |   Alpha    |  Beta      |   Gamma
==========================
1   | record-1   | record-1  |  record-1
2   | record-2   | record-2  |  record-2
3   | record-3   | record-3  |  record-3
.... .............      .........     ...........

** Write a php script to "INSERT" the records in the table
** Write a php/html script to "Select" all records in table format as given above.
** Write a JQuery script to color "Red" the first row of table.
** Write a JQuery script to color "Blue" the second row of table
** Write a JQuery script to color "Green" the third row of table